sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor John as 👤 John (Editor)
    actor Emma as 👤 Emma (Reviewer)
    actor Josh as 👤 Josh (Editor)
    actor Harry as 👤 Harry (MD / Release Mgr)
    participant System as Capell

    John->>System: Create "Q2 Product Launch" article
    John->>System: Save as Draft (Workspace: Open)
    Note right of System: Workspace stays Open<br/>Article not yet visible

    John->>System: Submit for approval
    System-->>Emma: 📧 "Action required: Q2 Product Launch needs your approval"
    Note right of Emma: Email includes<br/>Review & Approve CTA

    Emma->>System: Review article in workspace
    Emma->>System: Request changes (with notes:<br/>"Update pricing section + add CTA")
    System-->>John: 📧 "Workspace rejected: please revise"
    Note right of John: Workspace returns to Open<br/>Editable again

    Josh->>System: Open the workspace
    Josh->>System: Update pricing, add CTA
    Josh->>System: Save as Draft
    Josh->>System: Submit for approval (2nd round)
    System-->>Emma: 📧 "Action required: ... needs your approval"

    Emma->>System: Review changes
    Emma->>System: Approve (Workspace: Approved)
    System-->>Harry: 📧 "Workspace approved: Q2 Product Launch"
    System-->>Harry: 🔗 Signed preview link<br/>(auditable, expiring)

    Harry->>System: Open preview link
    Note right of Harry: Sees exact workspace state<br/>on public-facing site
    Harry->>System: Publish workspace
    System-->>John: 📧 "Workspace published: Q2 Product Launch"
    System-->>Emma: 📧 "Workspace published: Q2 Product Launch"
    System-->>Josh: 📧 "Workspace published: Q2 Product Launch"

    Note over John,Harry: Article is now live.<br/>Emergency rollback available<br/>to Harry if needed.
